function Start(flGameTime)

	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(idSelf, conv_PlayerInspectBody)
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(conv_PlayerGoToTown_A, idSelf)

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	idGuardClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(idGuard)
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(conv_FatherCallout, idSelf, idFather, idGuardClone)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idGuardClone, conv_FatherCallout)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idGuardClone, locGuardWalk, "NPC_Walk", false)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idGuardClone, 0.5)

end
